          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1691741583354-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1691741583354-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1691741583354-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chips are cooking, line a separate baking tray with <strong>tin foil</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>meat-free patty[ies]</strong> to the tray and put the tray in the oven for 10-12 min or until cooked through</p><p>Peel and finely slice your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Deseed your <strong>pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and slice into thin strips</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1691741589209-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1691741589209-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
