    {
      "instruction": "<p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Remove the pot from the heat and stir through the <strong>grated cheddar</strong> and <strong>umami seasoning</strong> – this is your <strong>cheese sauce</strong></p><p>Once the meat-free patty[ies] are cooked through, remove the tray from the oven and transfer the patty[ies] to a clean chopping board</p><p>Slice the <strong>meat-free patty[ies]</strong> into strips, then add them to the <strong>caramelised onion & pepper </strong>and mix it all together – this is your <strong>philly 'steak' filling</strong></p>",
